title: Group Therapy: Is An Ex An Ex For a Reason?
description: Jason is calling in because he is wondering an age old question, is an ex an ex for a reason?  Jason's college girlfriend has been reaching out to him lately and wants to get coffee but Jason doesn't know if he should just leave it in the past.
